data.description: Financing fell through! Embrace SOARING CEILINGS, huge driveway, fenced and gated back yard with huge patio! No HOA unlike most in the area! Walk to the factory. Nearby schools! Cool Springs and I65 very close. Lovely kid/pet friendly home.  Open floor plan. Living & dining room have soaring ceilings and hardwood floors with cozy fireplace. Kitchen is tiled w/new single basin sink & 2 pantries. Master bedrm w/hardwood floors and walk-in closet & standard closet. Master bathrm w/new marble vanity w/full bath. 2 Upstairs bdrms w/hardwood floors have Jack & Jill bathroom w/new marble vanity w/full bath. Bedrms are located in the back of the house, away from street. Very large bonus room w tall ceilings w/private entrance! Perfect for man/she cave, rental, play room, art room, bdrm. Storage shed. Selling as-is. Seller willing to credit $6,000 at closing for home insp repair costs, upgrades, etc. All furniture is negotiable.
